陳雲：特朗普在G7會議接受訪問，請香港人稍安毋躁，他認為香港將得到中國的好消息。特朗普在加稅逼迫之後，加上昨晚香港人勇武還擊特務兵團，中國終於面對現實。<br />
至於特朗普說香港的最終結局（ultimate outcome），我在文化沙龍再講啦。不過，大家都知道，最終成果，是我一貫主張的：中美共管香港，香港成為中美雙方的邦聯成員，變相獨立。<br />
//Trump: &quot;I think it's a very good word to use, 'calm.' Not a word that I use that often, but it's a good word to use. And I think it's one of the reasons its a great country... I really think that message is a good message with respect to what the ultimate outcome is in Hong Kong&quot;//

We, Hong Kongers, are united in strongly condemning Hong Kong Legislators who mislead the people of the United States, Senator &amp; Member of Congress, by claiming that we prefer to take care of themselves and do not welcome United States' &quot;interference&quot;. On the contrary, we need your support. <br />
<br />
The resistance movement in Hong Kong is a fight between the free world and the China dictatorship. We, Hong Kongers, hope U.S. Senator &amp; Member of Congress pass the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act, exert maximum pressure on Chinese Communist Party and force them to honour the promised political and human rights in &quot;Basic Law&quot; &amp; &quot;Sino-British Joint Declaration&quot;.<br />
<br />
We fully support the proposed Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act.<br />
<br />
U.S. Senator &amp; Member of Congress and foreign media, please don't waste your valuable time interviewing Hong Kong LegCo members who are the beneficiary of PRC rules and abuse of &quot;Basic Law&quot; &amp; &quot;Sino-British Joint Declaration&quot;. <br />
<br />
The so-called &quot;Pan-Democratic&quot; LegCo members have nothing to do with the democratic movement at all. They don't even dare to seek help from the U.S. nor U.K., and keep worried about CCP would disqualify them in the next LegCo election. <br />
<br />
Not to mention the so-called &quot;Independent&quot; (pro-Beijing) LegCo members, like Regina Ip Lau Suk-Yee, who is Beijing's puppet and agent undertaking PRC's order to suppress Hong Kongers' political and human rights.<br />
